    "Primarily, unstructured design specifications are transformed into a structured manner and given to the LLM as an input prompt to generate an SVA suite.",
    "The prompting is crucial in generating correct assertions.",
    "The RTL implementation is only used to simulate and identify syntax and simulation errors in generated assertions.",
    "The performance of ChIRAAG on OpenTitan design shows that an LLM is a good starting point to assist an engineer in assertion generation.",
    "We noticed only 27% of the generated SVA require refinement upon iterative prompting."
